## Session Start Checklist

Run this at the beginning of every session:

- [ ] Read `AGENTS.md` (or `CLAUDE.md` for Claude) if this is your first session
- [ ] Read `{{STATUS_FILE_PATH}}` for current task assignments
- [ ] Read `LEARNINGS.md` for any new knowledge from other AI sessions
- [ ] Identify your task and read the task file
- [ ] Read the context header files (max 6)
- [ ] Begin coding

---

## Session End Checklist

Run this at the end of every session:

- [ ] All tests pass: `{{PKG_MANAGER}} test`
- [ ] Build succeeds: `{{PKG_MANAGER}} build`
- [ ] `{{STATUS_FILE_PATH}}` updated with task progress
- [ ] Work log entry added via `/log` workflow
- [ ] `LEARNINGS.md` updated if you discovered something new
- [ ] No PROTECT LIST files modified
- [ ] Changes committed via `/commit` workflow
- [ ] Branch pushed if ready for review
